milestones.description: Kushal Malla has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (96) in an innings in ODIs for NEP, going past Paras Khadka's 66
Kushal Malla has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (10) in ODIs for NEP, going past Karan KC's 4
Kushal Malla has broken the record for most sixes (28) in ODIs for NEP, going past Rohit Paudel's 23
Bilal Khan has conceded the most runs in an innings (81) in ODIs for OMA, going past Bilal Khan's record of 68
This is the highest match aggregate (536) involving teams Nepal & Oman in ODIs
Rohit Paudel has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (45) for NEP, going past Sompal Kami
Lamichhane has become the fastest to 100 wickets in ODIs (42 matches), going past Rashid Khan's 44
